parameters:
Clea: There's no one here. I wonder if they're preparing
somewhere?

Imperial Soldier: G-Goblin horde! Someone, anyone, please
help!

Imperial Soldier: I-If we continue like this, we'll be
overrun!
Clea: Let's head outside the garrison!

General Atu: We managed to retreat without any trouble!
Hahaha, you've brought quite the extraordinary warriors!
Voice Priestess Phoni: I'm glad we made it in time...
Voice Priestess Phoni: Huh... That... C-Clea-san!?

Clea: Thank you so much... If you hadn't come... I would
have been in trouble...

Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes... Thanks to everyone from the
guild, we were able to safely bring her here.

Guild Leader Agonia: The situation seems to be worse than
expected.

Guild Leader Agonia: There is no doubt that Goblins have
gathered around the Monimos Mountain, as we encountered them
on our way here.

Swift Celis: ...We don't have much time. As soon as we're
ready, we should proceed with the operation.

General Atu: Yes, let me confirm the specific details of the
operation once again.

Sister Eleo: Please don't walk around on your own! Those who
were seriously injured, please be careful with your meals!

Sister Eleo: Alcohol is prohibited there! Honestly, you're
just like children!
Priestess Sophia: Thank you so much...

Sister Eleo: I promised, you know... I can be of help to
Sophia-san too!

Sister Eleo: Everyone, if you want to get your injuries
treated, please come talk to me, okay?

Imperial Soldier: The members of the academy have gathered
on the airship.

General Atu: We really appreciate your help with this
matter! Depending on the situation, there could have been
even greater damage.

General Atu: You guys will be summoned to the palace by
Caron, most likely... Hahaha, although it doesn't seem like
you have any desire for honor!

General Atu: There is no doubt that Clea is the greatest
contributor. We will cherish her and nurture her in the
Adventurer's Guild.

Guild Master Agonia: I understand, but right now you need
rest.

General Atu: That's right... Until you calm down, feel free
to use this place.

General Atu: I will return to the palace first! I look
forward to meeting you again on the battlefield!

One-armed Opro: I had a good experience. I look forward to
meeting you again somewhere in the future.
Mage Relm: Yes, I also think so.

One-armed Opro: Don't make that face... The end is the
beginning of something new...

One-armed Opro: Believe in Clea and do it. That's what it
means to be friends.
Mage Relm: Understood, thank you very much!

Adventurer Armada: I'm glad that there wasn't much damage in
Valier. On behalf of Valier, let me express my gratitude!
Thief Nora: Ah, I only fought!

Adventurer Armada: Ahaha, that's amazing! When you calm
down... come with Clea, okay?
Thief Nora: Yes! I will definitely go to meet you together!

Goat from the Bulk Brigade: That was an amazing battle
performance! The Bulk Brigade will remember you forever.
Thief Nora: Yes, thank you very much!

Goat from the Bulk Brigade: All exceptional warriors are our
friends! We pray that Clea will be able to walk again!

Thief Nora: I'll make sure to pass on the message to Clea-
san.

Cors the Wanderer: Well, as expected, everyone believed that
you would find a way to handle it somehow.

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, thank you for the wine, mmm... ah,
after a battle, it has an exceptional deliciousness!

Cors the Wanderer: Now that you've defeated the dragon, you
should make the most of this opportunity and sell your
charm.

Cors the Wanderer: I pray for Clea-san's early recovery, as
there are plenty of jobs that would be perfect for everyone
here.

Researcher Caron: I've had an amazing experience. I'll
return to the academy and start working on my research
paper!

Researcher Dokusa: I will also return to unravel the
conspiracy of the world! I am particularly interested in why
the dragon was born!

Mage Relm: I will return to the academy when the time is
right, but for now... I just need a little... more time.
Researcher Dokusa: Just stay by my side until I'm satisfied!
Mage Relm: Yes... Thank you very much.

Playboy Noble Lud Wow, you showed me something amazing! And
look at this invoice, it's quite impressive!
Maid Amina: It's the consequence of my own actions, Master.

Priestess Sophia: Looking back, I've been indebted to you in
various ways.

Playboy Noble Lud: Ahaha, don't worry about it! And as a
token of my gratitude, come and receive it from Clea-chan
and everyone else!
Priestess Sophia: Yes, I will definitely convey the message.

Imperial Soldier: Without General Atu's permission, I cannot
let you through.

Imperial Soldier: Let's fight together for the success of
the mission!
